                            <comment id="14469139" author="kons" created="Mon, 29 Mar 2010 16:13:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you please port this fix to the 1.6.x branch too?&lt;br/&gt;
Grails 1.2.2 recently updated to Groovy 1.6.8 which contains this feature (and now defect) as well.  I wouldn&apos;t expect Grails to be using 1.7 as quickly as they could a 1.6 update&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
